# Container SAST baseline — epic #448 / TRK-311 (Layer 1).
# Build context: helm/vector/projection-gate/. The Dockerfile COPYs
# verify_tenant_projections.py (init-container gate) + serve_metrics.py (metrics
# sidecar) from this context, so this baseline is a uniform hygiene floor that also
# keeps any stray .env / *.log out of the context upload.
/.git/
/.github/
/scripts/
/tests/
/docs/
*.md
*.log
.env*
